{"tid":1625630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲諗緊休息定唔休息既同我入撚哂嚟","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:50:01.000Z","uid":30991,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0bb0d17b86a2b9cc6d012492b430b312322472","tid":1625630,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"我真係屌撚哂你地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左休唔休息都可以屌一餐？ 仲話乜撚野兄弟爬山？而家出左兩條惡法 仲係度人咬人骨？<br />\n<br />\n想休息既咪休息 唔想休息既咪出去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勿分化啦 <br />\n<br />\n仲有開口埋口都要屌人地老母？ <br />\n<br />\n前線撚我明白你地成日點解咁撚燥 但係對住啲手足 唔該比返啲禮貌啦 下下都咁撚寸 <br />\n<br />\n真心你地咁樣就算前線定和理非既手足都會比你地屌到唔開心啦 <br />\n<br />\n但係唔會割啦當然和理非既手足都係一樣 我知你地好聽話 但係有時幫手做下其他野 <br />\n<br />\n買下物資 真係比個心出嚟得唔得 唔好只係企係度 叫下口號 唱下歌仔就算 <br />\n<br />\n仲有咪再唱啊～死黑狗！因為真係好撚煩，前線既手足會覺得好撚反感 因為真係出嚟打仗 真係出嚟抗爭<br />\n<br />\n唔好係度玩玩下咁得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地係商場唱 冇咩所謂 但係開戰前 完戰後 抖緊果陣 唔該你地唔好再唱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一係就唱啲激起戰憤既歌 求下你地真係咪撚再唱on9歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>咪再分化 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>各有各做 兄弟爬山</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bea3efdfc74d8551f4509583d12df61d24aab98c","tid":1625630,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhhhhhhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52247058c8d4bcd9772921540c4b8e5c4715d1